# S1 jump-SFX exercise: boot -> title -> Start -> GHZ1 -> run right + 8 jumps.
# No EXIT directive: the runner's --max-frames handles clean shutdown so the
# WAV header gets finalized.
WAIT 720
PRESS START 2
WAIT 400
HOLD RIGHT
WAIT 150
PRESS C 12
WAIT 90
PRESS C 12
WAIT 90
PRESS C 12
WAIT 90
PRESS C 12
WAIT 120
PRESS C 12
WAIT 120
PRESS C 12
WAIT 120
PRESS C 12
WAIT 120
PRESS C 12
WAIT 300
RELEASE
